scene_description: The background of the grid is comprised of black pixles. Sections of the grid are filled with randomly arranged pixels of a single color. This can be seen as the used space of a hardrive.
literal_instruction: The background of the grid is comprised of black pixles. Sections of the grid are filled with randomly arranged pixels of a single color. There is an empty void space, which can be filled with green pixels. The filled area must have flat sides, which always stay at least one pixel from the filled space.
